movie.title: Call of the Wild
movie.description_intro: In Montana, a young girl attracts the attention of an evil stranger after she rescues a hurt wolf.
movie.description_full: In Montana, a young girl attracts the attention of an evil stranger after she rescues a hurt wolf.

movies.title: Spies Like Us
movies.summary: Two low-level government employees, Emmitt Fitz-Hume (played by Chevy Chase) and Austin Milbarge (Dan Aykroyd), are chosen for a top-secret CIA mission. They are unsuitable as CIA agents but are deliberately chosen for this reason, as their mission is a decoy one and they are expendable. After being fast-tracked through training they are parachuted into Pakistan where all manner of adventures await them.

movies.title: Legend of the Guardians: The Owls of Ga'Hoole
movies.title_english: Legend of the Guardians: The Owls of Ga'Hoole
movies.title_long: Legend of the Guardians: The Owls of Ga'Hoole (2010)
movies.summary: Soren (Jim Sturgess), a young barn owl, is kidnapped by owls of St. Aggie's, ostensibly an orphanage, where owlets are brainwashed into becoming soldiers. He and his new friends escape to the island of Ga'Hoole, to assist its noble, wise owls who fight the army being created by the wicked rulers of St. Aggie's.

movies.title: Hui Buh: Das Schlossgespenst
movies.summary: Five hundred years ago, Hui Buh cheated in a card game, thus was turned into a ghost by thunder lighting. For all this time, he has lived in the castle alone without anyone to scare. Until when King Julius moves in for his wedding, Hui Buh knows he has to use every trick of his to keep the long-wasted ghost license.

movies.title: The Black Cauldron
movies.summary: Centuries ago, in the land of Prydain, a young man named Taran is given the task of protecting Hen Wen, a magical oracular pig, who knows the location of the mystical black cauldron. This is not an easy task, for The Evil Horned King will stop at nothing to get the cauldron.
